  "source": "Emitter oracle (Task P4): the fitted parameters, log-likelihood, AIC and the seeded ISimulatable draw are dumped from the REAL RMC.BestFit AutoRegressive MLE (Numerics @ a2c4dbf, RMC-BestFit @ fc28c0c) via tools/oracle_emitter and reproduced by tools/verify_oracles.py. Optimizer-dependent fit quantities carry rel 1e-8 (the C++/R/Python port reproduces the C# values to ~1e-13). The seeded draw is taken off the FITTED + pinned model (P3 arm); the fit-independent bit-identity of the MersenneTwister stream is proven separately in time_series_ar_sim.json at rel 1e-9.",
